The paper focuses on scene text detection using deep learning methods, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed model also involves instance segmentation and the use of semantic information, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of F-measure as a performance metric, which is commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
